Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但和鶴望蘭連結時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(926,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說是無意識地 依然成功適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,能想得到的只有...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,特殊樣本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個 在駕駛艙時有發生什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,莓她啊 在模擬戰之後 感覺有點不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才見到她時 好像在生氣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙從以前啊 只要牽扯到你的事反應都很激動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,莓有那樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,同為本來就寥寥可數的10字頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就像親兄妹那樣的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再算上我  三個人一直都寸步不離呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能一起從特殊班分發到這裡 簡直就是奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,兄妹嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,模擬戰那時 不是莓的錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,能由身為搭檔的你幫我轉達嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 那倒是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,廣 你現在打算怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次地 拜託Zero Two讓我操縱鶴望蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1462.667,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,廣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,關於她的事 你也聽說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人能和她搭檔超過三次的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,傳聞終究是傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和她搭檔的那些人下場如何 你也看到...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,倘若我真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,除了Zero Two以外無法和任何人搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那我該走的路只有一條
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是為了 操縱FRANXX而誕生於這世上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,結果 說可能讓廣成為操縱者的事後來呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1082.667,980)}Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只有起初能維持連結一陣子的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想必不太樂觀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙想也知道不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,和「那傢伙」戰成平手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又該如何評價呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那時未來突然跌倒的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啥? 你連當時自己說了什麼都不記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不重要的小事誰會記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會有你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以吵架唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,會影響數值的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 無法駕駛FRANXX的操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,始終都無法被爸爸們認同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1025.6,980)}賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在設施那時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家接二連三的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得有點不捨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呀 莓果然還是莓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明明身為隊長 會不會太照顧廣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真虧和她搭檔的五郎能忍到現在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,和五郎沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,廣要是當上操縱者 將會成為莫大的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因為這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那也要能「當上操縱者」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1129.6,980)}Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的可能性依然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,既然連和妳搭檔也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是認為沒戲唱了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他操縱了鶴望蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1094.4,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是在失去意識的狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候救了我們的仍然是他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信廣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,莓 我不是不能理解妳想袒護廣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但失去意識的廣就只是單純坐在裡面罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 還不能這樣下定論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 廣很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,即便在兩位數中也是出類拔萃的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(726,980)}菁英
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都曾經這麼想過的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,廣將會成為指引我們的路標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 現實並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1197.5,980)}Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,廣終究沒能成為操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經不再是那時候的廣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,妳也該接受事實了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟 妳也不想再見到那般掙扎的廣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling你真色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要一直盯著人家瞧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,博士有說過操縱者稍微好色點反而是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(793.6,980)}Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 怎樣算是好色...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等你等到睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?要去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這群孩子有被限制進出的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,像這裡基本上是完全禁止進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,S級通行許可?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個人一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 輕而易舉對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 妳會知道這種地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,放眼望去都是如出一轍的設計
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,無趣到了極點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我還是第一次進到都市裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,除了鳥籠和被允許的設施
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(790.667,980)}Mistilteinn
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們對其他地方根本一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼又一直盯著我看了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想適合妳的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擅長唷 幫別人取名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,唔~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦 我的話Zero Two就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(900,980)}Code
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 只叫號碼不是很乏味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我們啊 反正終究會死 被怎麼稱呼都沒差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這宛如遺骸般的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有天空也沒有海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,形同末路的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一起逃走吧 就我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我 能帶Darling離開這裡唷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,開~玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,本部下達了作戰指令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,誒!? 直、直接就是實戰了嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不用那麼緊張唷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,剛開始而已 不會讓你們面對之前那種等級的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1406.4,980)}莫霍級
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,原本還想讓你們多熟悉一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但看來情況不允許我們這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這次是康拉德級的叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(932.8,980)}Cornad
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:13.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}維克托·康拉德(1876-1962)20世紀地震學家，\N康拉德不連續面(Conrad discontinuity)即以其命名之。\N通常在大陸地殼各處深度在15到20公里之間，但在海洋地殼中則不存在。
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,體型比FRANXX小上許多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,叫龍會受到瑪格瑪能量反應吸引而現蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(825.333,980)}岩漿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而最近 自礦坑內層級8挖掘現場的最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(911.5,980)}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有叫龍出沒並破壞設施的情況發生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,已經達到自動防衛系統無法應付的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 關於這次的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭不會出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(825.6,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,從今以後 這座第13都市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,必須只靠你們來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,假使連這次的叫龍都無法驅逐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用想往後和其他叫龍的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,請各位在作戰時將這點銘記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,現場的指揮由015和056負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1001.6,980)}莓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1192,980)}五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,各自就啟動預備位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,還在想模擬戰的事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等等就要戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,整理一下思緒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我會當個好隊長的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,操縱就交給你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,總算輪到我們登場啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,慢著 你不要又一個人橫衝直撞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我就對啦 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,到底知不知道啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好了嗎 莓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎 吊蘭?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1150.4,980)}Chlorophytum
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,生野好像無法連結的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再給我一點時間 一下子就好!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不用試了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(475,980)}Chlorophytum
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吊蘭同步值未達啟動基準 持續下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(860,980)}Chlorophytum
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,吊蘭留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,其他三架正常出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這下又更棘手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的洞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟會通到哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,超酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,根本是管線組成的怪物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是從這裡抽取瑪格瑪燃料的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1061.333,980)}岩漿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1108,980)}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,直接下降至層級8
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然你們應該都很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想要徹底擊潰叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,除了針對它們被稱為心臟的「核」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1366.667,980)}Core
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,以各機體專用的瑪格瑪能量兵器直接破壞外別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(757.333,980)}岩漿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,必須要粉碎核心才能給予它們致命一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,開始移動至目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,各機體跟在翠雀後方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1061.333,980)}Delphinium
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,未來呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,了解~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,身體不舒服嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是那樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 生野妳從以前開始就偶爾會不穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不過明天還是去檢查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會是因為我們之間的適性出現了異常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這種情況一開始都會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不會因為這點事就解除搭檔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,已發現到叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,各機體就位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,部屬完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,作戰即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 比想像中小太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不能掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,照說好的戰術上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,到手啦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,帥啊!揃目!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,高興得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 看到了吧 本大爺的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 這姿勢很丟臉耶 別這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要輕敵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(861.5,980)}Core
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快將核徹底破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說是叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼了不起的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 未來 未來!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,未來 妳還好嗎 未來!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,未來 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還有另外一隻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不對...等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到 到底還有幾隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,先撤離這裡再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因為瑪格瑪能量的釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(858.667,980)}岩漿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,引來了大量的叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 妳看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始讓我去不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去好嗎 他們會全數陣亡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我和Zero Two前往支援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對非正式的雄式 是無法下達操縱許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(781.333,980)}Stamens
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不是說這種話的時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,留在現場的那些部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,會全滅唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快點讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和Darling動身出發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,出擊許可不會下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果廣不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就只剩我可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,滿...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 再不讓鶴望蘭出擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1002.667,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡的雄式操縱者只剩我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(960,980)}Stamens Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此當然只有我能去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭跟一般的FRANXX不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(604.5,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是沒有連結上...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,連站在那的廣都能操縱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,換做是我 更不可能有不行的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two 妳能和滿出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 你們是聽不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了我只想和Darling一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling也是這樣想的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妳和滿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我和其他人一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 既然Darling都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴上說的好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,事後再來反悔我可管不著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你操縱的那台鶴望蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1162,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就讓我來操縱給你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,或許在我內心深處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是期待著她拒絕那項提議的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(858.667,980g )}002
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,咦...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,未...未來!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,未來復活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,人家可沒死啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,未來 妳還好...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭前往支援了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(790.666,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能再支撐一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 只要撐到她來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,操縱鶴望蘭的是誰!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(905.333,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.28,Background,,0,0,0,,喂 莓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,集中精神...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,身體  突然沉重起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,莓!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等等!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛突然前傾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡守不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快回到礦坑中央處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在鶴望蘭抵達前先抵擋住...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(724,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多...不可能贏的了的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,現在該怎麼辦啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我剛剛沒有分心在不必要的事上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,或許情況不會演變成如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(656.5,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭也將能及時趕到支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是個失職的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(938.667,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,廣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家都先退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那個聲音 是滿嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,現場交由鶴望蘭接手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1026.667,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,其他成員全數撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 莓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 力量源源不絕地湧出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這種無所不能的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,單單搭檔的不同就有如此的差異
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,果然問題不在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能比廣還不如
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,廣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,多麼流暢的動作啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我甚至沒失去意識
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,能憑著自己的意志活動自如
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,乾脆這樣 直接讓我當妳的搭檔好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們肯定會成為最強的組合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就 稍微認真一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭 保持目前的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(713.333,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退作業結束了 接下來...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我去玩玩就回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快回來 Zero Two
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,準備進行鶴望蘭與其雄式的回收作業
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(790.4,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1094.133,980)}Stamens
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,愈快愈好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,回收...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們又被搭救一次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,想不到竟然是滿在操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是任何人的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是搭檔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,未...未來!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛是怎麼了 很不像妳唷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是因為聽到有援軍 一時鬆懈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,振作點啊 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只對著自己伸出的那支手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,笑靨背後的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,滿...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,傳聞是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看著那副模樣的滿 我不禁想到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,果然憑你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是無法成為我的Darling的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我的Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就只有你唷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1028,980)}016
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,當時 她是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能帶著我 離開這個地方
